dacs_handbook.title: Update board and work cycle descriptions.

comments.body:
### Tried so far

- Creating an app using the [initializr](https://start.spring.io/)
- Creating a new route
    - creating a MVCC test to assert that we get a 200 status response
    - authorizing anonymous users to access it with a `SecurityFilterChain`
    - accepting a parameter through RequestParam

### Questions
- How to deploy?  Compile a JAR, then [use capistrano to put the JAR in the current directory and restart a systemd service](https://gist.github.com/narkisr/39dbdd43046cfd1e1bd5)?
- 

### Answered questions

- Regular Spring or Reactive?  Best to use regular Spring, for each of troubleshooting, testing.
- Gradle or Maven? Maven, since we have experience on our team

comments.body:
The original fix when running `sudo nginx -s reload` generates more errors. 
We changed the nginxplus role in abid on line 24 from:
```
listen 443 ssl http2;
```
To look like:
```
   listen 443 ssl;

    http2 on;
```
We then tested this fix by running the playbook, and checking the site after to see if it was still up.
